short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use IRIS chrome to quickly extract questions from online questionnaires. Use Ask IRIS to get answers to your questions.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
IRIS Chrome is a helping tool for IRIS AI users to easily solve online questionnaire. IRIS Chrome provides Ask IRIS feature that enable users to ask question from their IRIS AI knowledge base without switch webpages.
IRIS Chrome comes up as a side panel tool to increase productivity during solving long questionnaires.
